banjammer
=========

banjammer is a daemon that monitors your logfiles for persistent
break-in attempts and adds firewall rules to reject further
connections from the same sources.

Requirements
============

banjammer only runs on Linux.  You will need GNU C++ to build it.

Installation
============

  ./configure
  make
  sudo cp banjammer.conf /etc   # and edit it to taste
  sudo make install

See 'man banjammer' for documentation.

